data.description: Discover your dream home in this spacious, generously upgraded residence built by Horizon View Homes in 2020. The heart of the home is the expansive kitchen, boasting double ovens and ample space for culinary creations and special gatherings.  Open to the living area offering a beautiful fireplace for warmth and ambiance.  The finished basement offers versatile living space with a bar, large rec area, and two oversized bedrooms, providing room for everyone to enjoy. Step outside to the inviting Xeriscape backyard, where an oversized patio awaits, perfect for outdoor entertaining or relaxation. With upgraded finishes throughout, this home exudes both style and comfort. Conveniently located within walking distance to schools, this home offers the ideal combination of quality, space, and location at an affordable price. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional residence your own.  See the list of upgrades in additional attachments!
